<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{هُزُوًا}</span> ... سُخْرِيَةً.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَقْرًا}</span> ... صَمَمًا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَوَاسِيَ}</span> ... جِبَالًا ثَابِتَةً.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَن تَمِيدَ}</span> ... لِئَلَّا تَضْطَرِبَ وَتَتَحَرَّكَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَبَثَّ}</span> ... نَشَرَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{زَوْجٍ كَرِيمٍ}</span> ... صِنْفٍ بَهِيجٍ نَافِعٍ حَسَنَ المَنْظَرِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْحِكْمَةَ}</span> ... الفِقْهَ فيِ الدِّينِ، وَالإِصَابَةَ فيِ القَوْلِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَهْنًا}</span> ... ضَعْفًا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَفِصَالُهُ}</span> ... فِطَامُهُ عَنِ الرَّضَاعَةِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَبِيلَ}</span> ... طَرِيقَ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
